Hello all-

Jason, Ken and I discussed this offline until we solved the mystery.

Jason&#39;s package has this parameter:

MutateDemolishLinkProbability

Which is a mutation operator that sets NEAT or CPPN links to zero. I had it
set to a positive value, which is why I was seeing a lot of zeros in NEAT
genomes. 


